media:group.media:title: Should TikTok Be Banned?
media:group.media:description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we ask a question that's been on the mind of numerous governments for well over a year. Should TikTok face a ban over "national security"? Given recent trends and the accusations made I can't help but wonder if this is a case of one side just feeling left out of the data gathering party. Thanks for watching!
